item.description:
With this integration a marketplace or an ecommerce platform can create transaction on behalf of a merchant.

In this model, Marketplaces and Platforms:

- Can create order and payments on behalf of merchants;

And the merchants:

- Pay Moip fees;
- Have liability over chargebacks;
- Have control over refunds;

