In this model, the marketplace continues as a primary receiver, however a secondary receiver is responsible for paying Moip fees.

In this model, Marketplaces:

- Have liability over chargebacks;
- Have control over refunds;

And the merchants:

- Receive part of the transaction;
- Pay Moip fees;

body.raw:
{
    "ownId": "{{$timestamp}}",
    "amount": {
        "currency": "BRL"
    },
    "items": [
        {
            "product": "Bicicleta Specialized Tarmac 26 Shimano Alivio",
            "quantity": 1,
            "detail": "uma linda bicicleta",
            "price": 2000
        }
